# core/landing.html
#: templates/core/landing.html:3
msgid "trackable. – Self-Hosted Time Tracking"
msgstr "trackable. – Self-Hosted Zeiterfassung"

#: templates/core/landing.html:4
msgid ""
"trackable. is an open-source, self-hosted time tracker for freelancers and "
"employees. Monthly tables, PDF export, email reports – all under your "
"control."
msgstr ""
"trackable. ist ein quelloffener, selbst-gehosteter Zeiterfasser für "
"Freelancer und Arbeitnehmer. Monatstabellen, PDF-Export, E-Mail-Berichte – "
"alles unter deiner Kontrolle."

#: templates/core/landing.html:21
msgid ""
"The time tracker you truly <strong style=\"color:var(--ctp-text)\">own</"
"strong>. No subscription, no cloud, no compromises &mdash; simply on your "
"own server."
msgstr ""
"Der Zeiterfasser, den du wirklich <strong style=\"color:var(--ctp-text)"
"\">besitzt</strong>. Kein Abo, keine Cloud, keine Kompromisse – einfach auf "
"deinem eigenen Server."

#: templates/core/landing.html:25 templates/core/landing.html:166
msgid "Go to Dashboard"
msgstr "Zum Dashboard"

#: templates/core/landing.html:38
msgid "Monthly report – February 2026"
msgstr "Monatsbericht – Februar 2026"

#: templates/core/landing.html:41
msgid "Mon, 03.02."
msgstr "Mo, 03.02."

#: templates/core/landing.html:45
msgid "Tue, 04.02."
msgstr "Di, 04.02."

#: templates/core/landing.html:49
msgid "Wed, 05.02."
msgstr "Mi, 05.02."

#: templates/core/landing.html:53
msgid "Thu, 06.02."
msgstr "Do, 06.02."

#: templates/core/landing.html:57
msgid "Fri, 07.02."
msgstr "Fr, 07.02."

#: templates/core/landing.html:61
msgid "Total February"
msgstr "Gesamt Februar"

#: templates/core/landing.html:75
msgid "Everything you need."
msgstr "Alles, was du brauchst."

#: templates/core/landing.html:75
msgid "Nothing you don't."
msgstr "Nichts, was du nicht brauchst."

#: templates/core/landing.html:76
msgid ""
"trackable. is lean, fast, and focused on the essentials – without bloated "
"SaaS features you'll never use."
msgstr ""
"trackable. ist schlank, schnell und auf die wesentlichen Dinge fokussiert – "
"ohne aufgeblähte SaaS-Features, die du sowieso nie nutzt."

#: templates/core/landing.html:82
msgid "Quick time entry"
msgstr "Schnelle Zeiterfassung"

#: templates/core/landing.html:83
msgid ""
"Enter start and end time, add your break – done. No tracking, no timer, no "
"stress."
msgstr ""
"Trag Start- und Endzeit ein, gib deine Pause an – fertig. Kein Tracking, "
"kein Timer, kein Stress."

#: templates/core/landing.html:87
msgid "Automatic monthly tables"
msgstr "Automatische Monatstabellen"

#: templates/core/landing.html:88
msgid ""
"Total hours and earnings are calculated automatically and displayed in a "
"clear table."
msgstr ""
"Gesamtstunden und Verdienst werden automatisch berechnet und übersichtlich "
"als Tabelle dargestellt."

#: templates/core/landing.html:92
msgid "PDF export"
msgstr "PDF-Export"

#: templates/core/landing.html:93
msgid ""
"Export your monthly tables as a professional landscape PDF – ready to submit "
"to your employer."
msgstr ""
"Exportiere deine Monatstabellen als professionelles PDF im Querformat – "
"bereit zum Einreichen beim Arbeitgeber."

#: templates/core/landing.html:97
msgid "Automatic email reports"
msgstr "Automatische E-Mail-Berichte"

#: templates/core/landing.html:98
msgid ""
"On the last day of each month you receive your monthly report automatically "
"by email."
msgstr ""
"Am letzten Tag jedes Monats erhältst du deinen Monatsbericht automatisch per "
"E-Mail."

#: templates/core/landing.html:102
msgid "Progressive Web App"
msgstr "Progressive Web App"

#: templates/core/landing.html:103
msgid ""
"Installable on your smartphone's home screen like a native app – no app "
"store needed."
msgstr ""
"Installierbar auf dem Homescreen deines Smartphones wie eine native App – "
"ohne App Store."

#: templates/core/landing.html:107
msgid "Multi-profile support"
msgstr "Multi-Profil-Support"

#: templates/core/landing.html:108
msgid ""
"Multiple jobs at once? No problem. Manage as many profiles as you need, each "
"with its own hourly rate."
msgstr ""
"Mehrere Jobs gleichzeitig? Kein Problem. Verwalte beliebig viele Profile mit "
"eigenem Stundenlohn pro Profil."

#: templates/core/landing.html:120
msgid "Your data."
msgstr "Deine Daten."

#: templates/core/landing.html:120
msgid "Your server."
msgstr "Dein Server."

#: templates/core/landing.html:120
msgid "Your control."
msgstr "Deine Kontrolle."

#: templates/core/landing.html:121
msgid ""
"trackable. runs entirely on your own infrastructure. No cloud, no "
"subscription, no vendor lock-in. You decide where your time tracking data "
"lives."
msgstr ""
"trackable. läuft vollständig auf deiner eigenen Infrastruktur. Keine Cloud, "
"kein Abo, kein Vendor-Lock-in. Du entscheidest, wo deine Arbeitszeitdaten "
"liegen."

#: templates/core/landing.html:123
msgid "Deploy with Docker in under 5 minutes"
msgstr "Deployment per Docker in unter 5 Minuten"

#: templates/core/landing.html:124
msgid "Compatible with Coolify, Portainer, and more"
msgstr "Kompatibel mit Coolify, Portainer und Co."

#: templates/core/landing.html:125
msgid "SQLite database with automatic backups"
msgstr "SQLite-Datenbank mit automatischen Backups"

#: templates/core/landing.html:126
msgid "No external tracking or analytics"
msgstr "Kein externes Tracking oder Analytics"

#: templates/core/landing.html:127
msgid "Fully open source on GitHub"
msgstr "Vollständig quelloffen auf GitHub"

#: templates/core/landing.html:139
msgid "Clone repository"
msgstr "Repository klonen"

#: templates/core/landing.html:143
msgid "Configure environment"
msgstr "Umgebung konfigurieren"

#: templates/core/landing.html:147
msgid "Launch the app"
msgstr "Starten"

#: templates/core/landing.html:150
msgid "trackable. is running on port 8000"
msgstr "trackable. läuft auf Port 8000"

#: templates/core/landing.html:162
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "Bereit anzufangen?"

#: templates/core/landing.html:163
msgid ""
"Set up trackable. in minutes and take control of your working time. Free, "
"forever."
msgstr ""
"Richte trackable. in wenigen Minuten ein und übernimm die Kontrolle über "
"deine Arbeitszeit. Kostenlos, für immer."

